OL,3,CMum's warning after biker killed in
OL,4,Cpetrol pump crash
OL,6,FThe mother of a motorcyclist who was
OL,7,Fkilled when he crashed into a petrol
OL,8,Fpump has warned: "This can happen to
OL,9,Fanyone."
OL,11,FDaniel Scott, 21, died at the scene of
OL,12,Fthe the crash at the BP garage in
OL,13,FColsterworth, Lincolnshire on 24 June.
OL,15,FIt happened after he left the main A1
OL,16,Fand drove down the slip road towards
OL,17,Fthe garage.
OL,19,FIn a statement, his mother Amanda
OL,20,FScott made a direct appeal to other
OL,21,Froad users.
