OL,3,CMum's warning after biker killed in
OL,4,Cpetrol pump crash
OL,6,FShe said: "This can happen to anyone,
OL,7,Fso be safe, think before you act and
OL,8,Fbe vigilant. While I know my words
OL,9,Fwon't stop more tragic road deaths
OL,10,Ffrom happening, I hope they will make
OL,11,Fpeople think as they take to the road.
OL,12,FAnything can happen."
OL,14,FMr Scott, who was from Durham, was a
OL,15,Fdeep-sea diver and train enthusiast,
OL,16,Fwho skydived out of planes in his
OL,17,Fspare time.
OL,19,FMs Scott described him as a "sensible,
OL,20,Fcaring and loving young man with his
OL,21,Fwhole life ahead of him".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
