OL,3,CMum's warning after biker killed in
OL,4,Cpetrol pump crash
OL,6,FShe said: "He was often quiet,
OL,7,Fparticularly around those he didn't
OL,8,Fknow ` but this hid an explosive
OL,9,Fpersonality and an insatiable passion
OL,10,Ffor life.
OL,12,F"Some might say he was a little
OL,13,Funusual, but he was such a happy
OL,14,Fperson ` from a young age he always
OL,15,Fhad a smile on his face and was loved
OL,16,Fby those who got to know him. And he
OL,17,Fwas a sensible young man too."
OL,19,FIn the statement she describes the
OL,20,Fmoment she was told about Daniel's
OL,21,Fdeath, saying her "heart stopped."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
