OL,3,CMum's warning after biker killed in
OL,4,Cpetrol pump crash
OL,6,FShe said: "When they told me I felt as
OL,7,Fthough my whole world was crumbling
OL,8,Faround me. I screamed. It's
OL,9,Findescribable. I never thought I would
OL,10,Flose my child so young, leaving behind
OL,11,Fa young brother and sister. He was a
OL,12,Frock to them and will be sorely missed
OL,13,Fby all of us. His death has hit our
OL,14,Ffamily so hard."
OL,16,FThe A1 was closed at Colsterworth for
OL,17,Fthe rest of the day following the
OL,18,Fcrash.
